<TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">From what I understand HD space is going to depend on how far you range with your character.  Someone at WP once likened the Arcane3D engine to an web browser.  It will download and display graphics and textures as it needs them and once it has grabbed them, store them to disk.  If you do not possess the model or texture the engine will display a closest match untill you finish downloading the specific one.  <P>Not sure if they are sticking to this model as they would end up paying for a lot of bandwidth but it is a neat idea.</FONT>
